Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:34.19,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Launching Fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:36.01,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:57.45,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Asumi’s Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Our country’s first manned exploratory space rocket, the Lion, was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:04.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,However, 72 seconds after liftoff…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the liquid fuel booster suddenly exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And although the Space Control Center activated what could be called its self-destruct system…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the flight suspension system did not function correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:24.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The Lion fell into an urban area and caused a huge disaster with many civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Five years later…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:43.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. I heard that Kamogawa’s wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.37,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. They said that the funeral is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:49.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She had been in that state for quite a while, hadn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.71,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:57.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Oh my, so that means it’s just father and child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.92,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,How sad for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.75,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:48.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I’m Suzunari, Asumi-chan’s teacher at Yuigahama Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei, have you seen Asumi around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:57.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Has something happened to Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…she took the cremated ashes and went off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:05.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can’t see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey mister, what’s your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,An advertising mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe someone from the circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You… You can tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don’t know, so that’s why I’m asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now this is surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can see me, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is it strange for me to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:18.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I am a ghost, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a strange old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It’s the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, don’t call me old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I look like this, I’m still young and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This T-shirt shows my fashion sense, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:33.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of reasons behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.04,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:41.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, what is that box that you’re carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This? Well you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It’s my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.39,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It’s Suzunari-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, will you be here tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:11.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Great! Bye-bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn’t ask for your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My name? Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Lion-san? What a weird name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wa… Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.52,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Who was she talking with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan, were you with someone back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He said he was a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion? A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.88,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I just can’t seem to keep up with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.43,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Suzunari-sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Truly, my condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:30.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for causing so much trouble today, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you that this was something very important, didn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,These ashes aren’t a toy to be played with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening, Asumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:50.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I guess being a single father is just no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.77,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She doesn’t listen to a thing I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That’s not…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She may not truly feel that her mother has passed away…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:08.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…because when Asumi became old enough to be aware of things…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…my wife was already in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I had to raise my daughter without her knowing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. It’s rude of me to ask…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but what kind of person was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you remember it as well, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The rocket explosion incident five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My wife was a victim of that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi was still only one year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:39.35,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My wife received grave wounds on her face and head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:45.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,In the end, she passed away without regaining consciousness even once in those five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.52,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi once said that she’d like to be able to see her mother just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That was last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.99,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After all, she had never seen her mother’s face, except in pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.99,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,But ever since that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi hasn’t spoken once about her mother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,At that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…what Asumi was thinking, how she felt…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So all that has happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother became a star too, didn’t she, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:38.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. That’s what I think happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A star, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, you came to see me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It’s summer vacation right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a lot of free time yourself, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It’s not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is Suzunari-sensei nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Lion-san, do you know Suzunari-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No, it’s just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I happened to see her yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes she gets a lonely expression…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,A very lonely expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The stairs here are so long they really take their toll on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My silly son must be pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Every year at Obon…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:22.80,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,Note: Obon is an annual Buddhist ritual in July or August to honor the spirits of a family’s ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…he has such a pretty woman come visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:30.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That’s right, today is the day of the Yuigahama fireworks display, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That boy wrote in a composition in elementary school…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:39.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…that his dream was to watch fireworks from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:46.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Afterwards I heard from someone else that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.29,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, it’s pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:53.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But without even realizing that, that boy went on to be an astronaut…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He really was a silly boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:59.42,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It’s already been five years since then, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going, Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You’ll help me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Already five years since then, huh?
Comment: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:36.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:35.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch (A-F)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This is a figure of the Lion’s mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can have it, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It’s just a little trinket they sell at the space center’s gift shop, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What, just a trinket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it’ll make a good memento, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don’t be saying things like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,To someone who’s going up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! I’m really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You really do get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just one week left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It’s pretty amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The youngest astronaut ever…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuko…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:31.22,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight safely…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Then, I’d like for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that’s okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Now you’ve got me wondering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I’ll tell you after I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Say it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I’ll make sure to tell you when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,No good, it has to be now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why in the world did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A memento…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty bad joke, wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Asumi-chan’s father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:25.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Asumi-chan took the ashes and disappeared again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:35.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’m tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you’re supposed to be younger than you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:45.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,These remains are as heavy as a person to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Talking nonsense like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But do you want to rest for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could you play that thing from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Out of all the instruments…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the harmonica was the first one to fly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:47.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. In 1965, the pilot of the American capsule, Gemini VI…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,…wore a 3cm wide harmonica around his neck when he went up into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:56.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And then he sent a present of music down to Earth from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you sure know a lot about space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But the Earth must be really pretty when you see it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:13.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’ll never be able to see it since I ended up like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:17.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, could you really be a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just once would have been fine, but I sure wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.44,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan! Answer me if you’re there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! There’s a great view of it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Suzunari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn’t seem to be out here by the shore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:21.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she might have come to the booths down here, so I asked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But no one said that they had seen Asumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:27.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I’ll look around here one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mom will be happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I’m sure she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:57.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, I have a favor to ask of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That’s fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did you go, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.59,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This couldn’t be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:21.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Really… where could she have wandered off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.27,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should contact the police now…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The door was locked, so I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.74,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’m sure I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That’s not a toy, it’s something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:57.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And yet you still keep running off with it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Those ashes are..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They’re the ashes of my mother who gave birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If you understand that, then why…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:13.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I buried them in the place with the prettiest view of the Yuigahama Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She seemed so lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:26.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Closed up in that dark hospital room…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:31.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then she got put in a little box when she died..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I felt so sorry for Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.59,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You said it yourseIf, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:42.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You said Mom always loved the Yuigahama Bay, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well… was Mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…happy to see the ocean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:08.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,These stairs are so long, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You found Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I’m very sorry to have worried you, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:27.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Asumi said that she had something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.14,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hello, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Sensei, do you know Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:40.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san said that he had something he wanted me to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:49.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,“Don’t be too mean to the Lion doll, Yuuko.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,See ya, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He’s the only one who knows about this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Takano-kun..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight safely. I d like for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:09.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:19.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That’s mean, going and becoming a star by yourself..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:23.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Takano-kun, that’s mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.10,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:34.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:37.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe he’s not here today…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:42.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you fly to space on a rocket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:46.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I’m going to be a rocket driver{pilot}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll let you ride for free, Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:53.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So let me hear lots more stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:55.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:36.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Winter of the third year of middle school…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.39,0:24:38.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We have to be deciding our futures now…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:40.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but I’m still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.93,0:24:43.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to attend Tokyo Space University…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:45.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…and learn to be an astronaut…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:47.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but I’m sure that my dad will be against it…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:53.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And it takes lots of money, so I think that maybe I should give up on that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:57.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: Asumi’s Dream.